    {
      "name": "无效场 无效器发出一个无效场，在10英尺的半径内抑制魔法。 (Nullifying Field: The nullifier emits a nullifying field that suppresses magic in a 10-foot radius)",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A creature in that area that is concentrating has disadvantage on Constitution saving throws to maintain concentration. In addition, when a creature in that area casts a spell of 1st level or higher, or activates a magic item effect that deals damage, restores HP, teleports, or imposes a condition, it must first succeed on a DC 15 Spellcasting ability check or the effect fails, but the spell slot, charge, or other resource is still expended.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
